quran[15{c,v,t}:
21,58,chunancha is ne unn ko tukre tukre kar diya aur sirf un ke barray ko chore diya taakay shayad woh is ki taraf rujoo karen
21,59,"( onhon ne aa kar buton ka yeh haal dekha to ) kehnay lagey"" hamaray khudaon ka yeh haal kis ne kar diya? bara hi koi zalim tha woh """
21,60,"( baaz log ) bolay"" hum ne aik nojawan ko un ka zikar karte suna tha jis ka naam ibrahim hai """
21,61,"unhon ne kaha"" to pakar lao ussay sab ke samnay taakay log dekh len ( uss ki kaisi khabar li jati hai ) """
21,62,"( ibrahim ke anay par ) onhon ne poocha"" kyun ibrahim, to ne hamaray khudaon ke sath yeh harkat ki hai? """
21,63,"uss ne jawab diya"" balkay yeh sab kuch un ke is sardar ne kya hai, inn hi se pooch lau agar yeh boltay hon """
21,64,"yeh sun kar woh log apne zameer ki taraf palty aur ( apne dilon mein ) kehnay lagey"" waqai tum khud hi zalim ho """
21,65,"magar phir unn ki mat palat gayi aur bolay"" too jaanta hai ke yeh boltay nahi hain """
21,66,"ibrahim ne kaha"" phir kya tum Allah ko chore kar unn cheezon ko pooj rahay ho jo nah tumhe naffa pohanchanay par Qadir hain nah nuqsaan"
21,67,"taf hai tum par aur tumahray inn mabodon par jin ki tum Allah ko chore kar pooja kar rahay ho kya tum kuch bhi aqal nahi rakhtay? """
21,68,"unhon ne kaha"" jala daalo is ko aur himayat karo apne khudaon ki agar tumhe kuch karna hai """
21,69,"hum ne kaha"" ae aag, thandhi ho ja aur salamti ban ja ibrahim par """
21,70,woh chahtay thay ke ibrahim ke sath buraii karen magar hum ne un ko burii terhan nakaam kar diya
21,71,aur hum ne ussay aur loot ko bacha kar uss sarzamen ki taraf le gay jis mein hum ne duniya walon ke liye barkaten rakhi hain
21,72,"aur hum ne usay ishaq ataa kya aur yaqoob is par mazeed, aur har aik ko Saleh banaya"
